Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.90,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,A World Dai Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:12.08,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I know you'll be one someday, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:13.66,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.00,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Even at the audition the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.95,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\fnArial\fs14\3c&HB0C4E5&\4c&HB0C4E5&\c&H5D5D5D&}Regarding Your Audition\N\N{\3c&HF5F5F3&\4c&HF5F5F3&}Hello, Kokona Otori-sama.\NThank you very much for auditioning with us.\NAfter careful deliberation, we regret to inform you that\N{\fs20}you have not passed {\fs14}our audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.95,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,they told me I lacked Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.82,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I{\i0} disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.84,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You don't believe them either,\N do you, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.99,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:36.10,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Do you know what kind of people \Nbecome World Dai Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:38.41,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:43.11,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,People who are really good at acting... \Nand singing and dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:47.05,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,People so dazzling that you just \Ncan't take your eyes off of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.97,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's not it at {\i1}all{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.99,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They're people who believe\N in their future selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:07.38,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can hear them, can't you? \NThe voices calling your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.75,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll ever make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.77,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Can I really become a World Dai Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.27,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You will, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:37.02,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.38,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,In the twentieth century,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.71,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,the passionate performances of actors\N who appeared like shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:53.60,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,ushered the world into \Nthe great age of theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:55.63,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(270,190)\fnTimes New Roman\fs15\shad0\c&H2E314E&\3c&HECECEC&\pos(307.2,239.6)}Kaminarimon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:59.67,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,It became the ultimate entertainment \Nfor the masses around the globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:03.67,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,and many an actor competed \Nfor the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:13.82,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Performers with the Sense to outshine others\Nbecame known as "Dai Stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.02,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,And the pinnacle of Dai Stars\N was given the title...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.71,Main - Italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,World Dai Star.
