Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.58,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What are you so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.75,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I mean, who wouldn't be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.40,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to join SIRIUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.93,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,and I've already gotten\N two tryout rejections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.59,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,There you go getting down on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:55.80,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You've rehearsed loads for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.78,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,so you need to go in full of confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hup...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.16,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I finally got to a callback, \Nso I've gotta do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.78,Main,Kokona's Mother,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.84,Main,Kokona's Mother,0,0,0,,Here's your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.30,Main,Kokona's Mother,0,0,0,,You can't project properly\N on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.30,Main,Kokona's Father,0,0,0,,Leave no room for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.92,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.60,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.88,Main,Kokona (Romeo),0,0,0,,Like a rich jewel in an Ethiope's ear;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.57,Main,Kokona (Romeo),0,0,0,,Beauty too rich for use, for earth too dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:45.57,Main,Kokona (Romeo),0,0,0,,Did my heart love till now?\NForswear it, sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:50.44,Main,Kokona (Romeo),0,0,0,,For I ne'er saw true beauty till this night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:55.46,Main,Kokona (Romeo),0,0,0,,Forsooth... this is true love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.33,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You're overacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.16,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.56,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You sound more like a fool than a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.32,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Romeo's actually quite the playboy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.50,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,yet in this moment, he feels his destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.85,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,He'd probably sound way more exhilarated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.22,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Destiny? Exhilarated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.99,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.72,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,True! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.22,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Congrats. Now you're a bigger fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.12,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I just don't get it. \NI've never been in love before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:33.12,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You've never been a murderer\N or a detective either, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.37,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But even so, an actor must\N play those roles convincingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.51,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Then how would you do the scene, Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.14,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:59.54,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Did my heart love till now? \NForswear it, sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:04.39,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,For I ne'er saw true beauty till this night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.89,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Forsooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.29,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is true love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.94,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Whoa! That was amazing, Shizuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.56,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} supposed to be doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:36.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,If only you could \Naudition too, Shizuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.26,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Come on. The first train will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.64,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:59.58,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fay.24\fnTimes New Roman\fs30\shad0\bord1\frx8\fry14\3c&H3B386B&\4c&H121030&\frz356.9\move(429.6,153.733,403.133,153.733)}Elisabeth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:59.58,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fay.19\fnTimes New Roman\fs20\shad1\bord1\move(465.067,238,438.6,238)\frx8\fry14\frz358.4\3c&H121030&\4c&H121030&}Now Playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:59.59,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Elisabeth{\i0} is playing again. \NI wonder if we can get tickets the day of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.59,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,There's an audition for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.46,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You'll pass, so it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}me{\i0} auditioning, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:11.72,Subtitles,Kathrina subs,0,0,0,,The metro... Which one goes to... Asakusa?
