Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.22,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs10\shad0\bord0\an3\c&HADAB92&\b1\pos(153.2,186.266)}Tokyo   Hamamatsucho  Shinagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.22,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs10\shad0\bord0\an3\c&HADAB92&\b1\pos(116.934,212.933)}Kawasaki   Yokohama       Kannai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.85,Subtitles,Kathrina subs,0,0,0,,It's basically a maze...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.31,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Konnichiwa! Um, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Guten Tag? Добрый день?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Bonjour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.14,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Merci!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.20,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That means "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:37.29,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Guten Tag. I'm German, but you \Ncan speak to me in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.79,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:43.67,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So... where are you headed? \NI'll be happy to show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.72,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.84,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Asakusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.31,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Asakusa?! We're headed there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:51.87,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.68,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Come on! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.18,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.71,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.44,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs12\fnArial\b1\shad0\frx0\fry346\pos(251.2,191.066)\frz0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7F52A9&}Won't You Be a {\c&H4B35BE&\3c&HE1E4FC&}Dai Star, {\3c&H7F52A9&\c&HFFFFFF&}too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.79,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, what did you come to see today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.69,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.60,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're going to Asakusa, \Nso I figure you're seeing a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.89,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It has over a hundred theaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.16,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Is anything super popular right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:15.16,Subtitles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(101.733,122.6)}Did you make it to Japan safely?\NTell me if you pass or fail your audition immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.15,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Maybe... {\i1}Mecha Macbeth Versus Space Hamlet{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.38,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, what is it, Kathrina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.79,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.12,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.28,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.22,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,When's the train coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.42,Main,Mother,0,0,0,,It'll be here soon. Just keep \Nreading your picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.18,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(331.733,76.4)\fnImpact\fscx200\c&H231AD7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1}Little Red Riding Hood
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.18,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Do you like "Little Red Riding Hood"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.59,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Then I'll perform it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.74,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you an actress, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:50.98,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh... Not yet, but I hope to be someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.01,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:08:00.26,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, there was a little girl \Nwho wore a cap of red velvet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.50,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\shad0\c&H694A40&\3c&HEFF5F2&\pos(320,42.267)\b1}Kaminarimon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.13,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\shad0\c&H694A40&\fs14\3c&HEFF5F2&\b1\pos(322.667,130.8)}Kaminarimon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.13,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Welcome to Asakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.63,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh... It's much noisier \Nthan where I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.64,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.65,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Thanks for leading me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.09,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What? I can take you to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.98,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll use my navigation app from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.77,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.28,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.02,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.133,130.267)\fnTimes New Roman\shad0\b1\c&H0E0A06&\3c&HCCBDBB&}Nakamise {top}
