Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.94,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs14\b1\shad0\c&H382122&\3c&HF3F4F6&\frx352\fry310\pos(569.068,59.868)\frz16.32}Koyama Shop {right 8:27}
