Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:39.58,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'll get as much on me as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:43.79,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs14\shad0\bord0\c&H8331AE&\frx6\fry18\frz355.8\pos(328,39.599)}Hanayashiki Street
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.54,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:50.31,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going that way too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.66,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Also, the theater playing \N{\i1}Mecha Mac{\i0} is the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.18,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I know that. I'm going to the Sirius Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.10,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sirius...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.54,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wait, are you auditioning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.20,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.52,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The Sirius Theatre!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.93,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Home of the female acting troupe SIRIUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:13.32,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,founded by Japan's renowned \NWorld Dai Star, Shamo Yamabuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.88,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You said you saw your first play here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.93,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.90,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The SIRIUS troupe mainly does musicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.71,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,They're so elegant and wonderful!\NI've seen them so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:28.89,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This is where I first realized\N I wanted to be an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.66,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So you're auditioning, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.58,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.10,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Talk about a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.36,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's nice to formally meet you.\N I'm Kokona Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:42.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Let's do our best so we can stand on \Nthat stage together, Kathrina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:48.72,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm not going to shake your hand. \NI'm fairly certain I won't see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.73,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:54.22,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, \Nyou have no Sense whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:02.99,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)\fnArial\shad0\b1\frx-5\bord0\fs36\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(321.456,128.969)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.18,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The heck is her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.69,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She may be cute,\N but she's got a rotten personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:21.00,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"I'm not going to shake your hand. \NI'm fairly certain I won't see you again."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.30,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Honestly, how nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That was great, Shizuka-chan! \NYou're so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:30.04,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one she mocked. \NWhy are you so calm about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.23,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.97,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,My Sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.49,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an7\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H752955&\3c&HC48CB0&\pos(163.6,218)}\h\hNoa Hiiragi\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.49,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an9\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H752955&\3c&HC48CB0&\pos(147.6,77.199)}\h\hSIRIUS VP\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.48,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Welcome to auditions for SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.61,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's Hiiragi-san! The former Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:51.51,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We are currently looking for talent\N to become SIRIUS Dai Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:57.65,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Talent we can nurture into a World Dai Star\N to take the globe by storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:04.05,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing\N your acting Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:11.13,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We will now begin auditions,\N so please gather at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:18.37,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You've been practicing even \Nmore since you met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.30,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can do this, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.40,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Believe in me. And yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:40.42,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get amazing pictures of my \Nfuture juniors at their audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:40.42,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an9\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H823A45&\3c&HDDB3B8&\pos(474.001,125.733)}\h\hPanda Yanagiba\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:40.42,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an3\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H823A45&\3c&HDDB3B8&\pos(519.334,93.199)}\h\hSIRIUS Member\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.68,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Hmm... This one's too pretty\N and this one's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.18,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Reverse corrections.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.28,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Making sure their privacy is safe and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:52.78,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Yup! I'm definitely the cutest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:12:00.07,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an2\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H606C2F&\3c&HDCEBB8&\pos(384.4,54.267)}\h\hSIRIUS Member\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:12:00.07,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an8\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H606C2F&\3c&HDCEBB8&\pos(494.267,146)}\h\hChisa Sasuga\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.92,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Acting's not about your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:55.98,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.66,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,That just sounds like sarcasm coming\N from a pretty girl like you, Sassu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.78,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Also, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.30,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,It's great when they loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.63,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,The noodles? Or your nerves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:16.42,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an9\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H215B36&\3c&HCAF2D7&\pos(547.6,95.334)}\h\hSIRIUS Director\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:16.42,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,1)\bord4\an9\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H215B36&\3c&HCAF2D7&\pos(498.666,232.933)}\h\hHana Kudo\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:16.42,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,This is our fifth audition, but we still \Nhaven't found our diamond in the rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:21.46,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,Kathrina Griebel, \NTobias and Theresa's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.71,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,I guess we're lucky to even have her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.13,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's got {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.12,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's finally time to see everyone's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.90,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They said you'd find out the role the day of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:41.62,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll now proceed with the readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.66,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll also be handing out your scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.95,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:51.62,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\shad0\bord0\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H372616&\b1\pos(200.934,61.467)\frz0.307}The Little Mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.62,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,SIRIUS's {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.61,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You've totally practiced this one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.43,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.36,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Act 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.32,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The Little Mermaid swims to \Nthe Sea Witch's lair
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.64,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,and asks to be made into a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.42,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The Sea Witch promises to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.68,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,in exchange for her beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.54,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who's the Sea Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.56,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'll be reading the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san's doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.07,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You can keep your scripts with you.\NCome up onto the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.01,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Let's start with number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.38,Main,Auditionee C,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.43,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Reading with Hiiragi-san, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.94,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I wonder if the boss plans to fail them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.87,Main,Auditionee C,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.67,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.33,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Let's get started, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:47.66,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Once you become human, \Nyou can never be a mermaid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:53.40,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,And should the prince marry another girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.69,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,your heart will be ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.77,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Without even a moment to repent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.43,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,you'll disappear into sea-foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:09.70,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Do you still want to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.41,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,I'm asking you if you're prepared for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:20.67,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.38,Main,Auditionee D,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.08,Main,Auditionee D,0,0,0,,I'm prepared... S-Sea Witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:28.87,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:34.36,Main,Auditionee E,0,0,0,,I'm prepared! Sea Witch,\N what do you require of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.38,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.48,Main,Auditionee F,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.70,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,If they can't keep up with Hiiragi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:41.78,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,they can't express the \NLittle Mermaid's true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:46.14,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But if they push too much, \Nthey come off too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.63,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This is what a Dai Star's acting looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:55.19,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next, number 16. Kathrina Griebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:36.21,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No set. Not even a backdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.63,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Only a small spotlight \Nshining on center stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:45.39,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,She's hiding in the shadows to capture\N the Sea Witch's unpredictability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.14,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No wonder the girls can't hold their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.39,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But they're all third-rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.08,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm ready whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:15.03,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Once you become human, \Nyou can never be a mermaid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:21.15,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,And should the prince marry another girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.46,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,your heart will be ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.30,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Without even a moment to repent,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.86,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,you'll disappear into sea-foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.88,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Do you still want to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.36,Main,Kathrina (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:39.94,Main,Hiiragi (Sea Witch),0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}truly{\i0} certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.18,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Did she forget her lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.94,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,No, she's still in character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:03.45,Main,Kathrina (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,I'm prepared! Sea Witch,\N what do you require of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.46,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,That pause was impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:14.49,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,She used the spotlight to her advantage, \Ntransforming from the Little Mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.73,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,to a woman in love with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.72,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I think we found our promising new talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.43,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Thank you. You can head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.53,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next up is our last candidate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.72,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.41,Main - Top,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You've got this, Kokona. You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:35.85,Main - Italics,Kokona,0,0,0,,What do I do?\NMaybe I can't do this... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.55,Main - Top,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You're going to be a Dai Star, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.43,Main - Top,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.03,Main - Italics,Kokona,0,0,0,,don't have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.68,Flashback - Italics,Judge A,0,0,0,,You have no Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.42,Flashback - Italics,Judge B,0,0,0,,You're not bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.97,Flashback - Italics,Judge C,0,0,0,,In this day in age, you have to have Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.46,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.45,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Can't play the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.37,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.29,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You mustn't look so scary, Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.83,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Everyone will tense up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.78,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yae? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:05.56,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,430)\bord4\an9\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H5A145C&\3c&HC690C4&\pos(484.667,82.001)}\h\hSIRIUS Member\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:05.56,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,430)\bord4\an7\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H5A145C&\3c&HC690C4&\pos(498.534,222.267)}\h\hYae Niizuma\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.69,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I came to rehearse \Nfor our next performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.64,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,but I can't find Panda-san or the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.09,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,so I'm looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.71,Main,Auditionees,0,0,0,,It's Yae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.12,Main,Auditionees,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:17.89,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Miss, would you mind if I \Ndid this scene with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.17,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.69,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:24.64,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's only natural to help those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.95,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,That's what will lead to world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.84,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.09,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.22,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If Yae's involved, we'll \Nneed to make some changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.43,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You'll be playing the Little Mermaid, Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.49,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.43,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.22,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Act 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:52.96,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The prince tells the Little Mermaid\N he's to be engaged in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:57.58,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,He's marrying a princess from a neighboring \Nkingdom who saved him from drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:02.55,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The Little Mermaid longs to tell him\Nit was really her, but she has no voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:06.50,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,She tries desperately to convey her \Nfeelings, yet can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.83,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You'll be playing the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:15.87,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,This is the crucial emotional moment\N leading up to the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.69,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,One wrong step,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.59,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,and the audience's hate for the\N moronic prince will ruin the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.26,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san's being cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.59,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,That's what I love about the boss, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.84,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,What kind of performer\N do you want to be, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.35,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,If you focus too much on being "good,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:37.11,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,you'll get so stiff you won't be able to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:41.71,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,What's important is what\N {\i1}you{\i0} want to be onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.30,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What {\i1}I{\i0} want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:49.00,Main - Top,Niizuma (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,The world you've shown me \Nis just so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.05,Main - Top,Niizuma (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,If only I could tell you how I really feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.31,Main - Italics,Kokona,0,0,0,,What I've wanted to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.60,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They're people who believe\N in their future selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.53,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,What is it? What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.55,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,I know! You must be happy for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.60,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,I'm just the luckiest man alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:19.61,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,To think that the princess \Nwho saved me that stormy night
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.24,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,is going to marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.75,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,She wasn't like that at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:28.37,Main,Niizuma (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,No... {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.33,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.24,Main,Niizuma (Little Mermaid),0,0,0,,I'm the one who saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.00,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.25,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,Did something painful happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.29,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,Are you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.01,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.26,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:54.78,Main,Kokona (Prince),0,0,0,,I'll always be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:21:00.46,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I told you so. \NI knew you could do it, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:12.06,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.63,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Were you waiting around \Njust to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:19.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah! If it weren't for you,\NI would've been sent packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:20.80,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.56,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm Yae. Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.40,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:30.39,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Even if I don't pass this round,\NI'm going to audition for SIRIUS again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.29,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,And then, one day we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.42,Main - Top,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Hey, Kokona! Why are you talking \Nlike you're going to fail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.25,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hey! This part's really \Nimportant, so butt out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.18,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:54.11,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona Otori played the prince \Nfrom {\i0}The Little Mermaid{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.31,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:22:00.40,Main - Top,Kokona,0,0,0,,Just thinking about what I'd have\N done if Yae-chan hadn't shown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.94,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,That wasn't her take on the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.96,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Who exactly were you playing?
